maml:description.maml:para: Gets a list or a particular NotificationHub description.
Get-AzureNotificationHub cmdlet gets a list of all NotificationHubs under a Namespace or a specified NotificationHub within the namespace.
Gets a list or a particular Authorization Rule description associated with the specified NotificationHub.
Get-AzureNotificationHubAuthorizationRules cmdlet gets a list of all the Authorization Rules descriptions or a specified Authorization Rule associated with the NotificationHub specified.
Gets the Primary and Secondary ConnectionString of a particular NotificationHub Authorization Rule.
Get-AzureNotificationHubListKeys cmdlet gets the Primary and Secondary ConnectionString of a particular NotificationHub Authorization Rule.
Gets the NotificationHub PNS credentials
Get-AzureNotificationHubPNSCredentials cmdlet gets the PNS credentials for a particular NotificationHub.
Gets a list or a particular Namespace description.
Get-AzureNotificationHubsNamespace cmdlet gets a list of all Namespaces of type NotificationHub under a subscription or specified resource group.
Gets a list or a particular Authorization Rule description associated with the specified Namespace.
Get-AzureNotificationHubsNamespaceAuthorizationRulescmdlet gets a list of all the Authorization Rules descriptions or a specified Authorization Rule associated with the Namespace specified.
Gets the Primary and Secondary ConnectionString of a particular Namespace Authorization Rule.
Get-AzureNotificationHubListKeys cmdlet gets the Primary and Secondary ConnectionString of a particular Namespace Authorization Rule.
Creates a new NotificationHub
New-AzureNotificationHub cmdlet creates a new Namespace.
Creates new NotificationHub Authorization Rule
New-AzureNotificationHubAuthorizationRules cmdlet creates a new NotificationHub Authorization Rule.
Creates a new Namespace.
New-AzureNotificationHubsNamespace cmdlet creates a new Namespace of type NotificationHub.
Creates new Namespace Authorization Rule
New-AzureNotificationHubAuthorizationRules cmdlet creates a new Namespace Authorization Rule.
Removes an existing NotificationHub.
Remove-AzureNotificationHub cmdlet removes existing NotificationHub.
Removes an existing NotificationHub Authorization Rule.
Remove-AzureNotificationHubAuthorizationRules cmdlet removes an existing NotificationHub Authorization Rule.
Removes an existing Namespace.
Remove-AzureNotificationHub cmdlet removes existing Namespace of type NotificationHub.
Removes an existing Namespace Authorization Rule.
Remove-AzureNotificationHubsNamespaceAuthorizationRules cmdlet removes an existing Namespace Authorization Rule.
Sets the PNS credentials and other properties for a NotificationHub.
Set-AzureNotificationHub cmdlet sets the PNS credentials and other properties for a NotificationHub.
Sets the Authorization Rules for a NotificationHub.
Set-AzureNotificationHubAuthorizationRules cmdlet sets a NotificationHub Authorization Rule.
Sets the Namespace properties.
Set-AzureNotificationHubsNamespace cmdlet sets the Namespace properties. This would mainly be to enable/disable a namespace and to make a namespace critical.
Sets the Authorization Rules for a Namespace.
Set-AzureNotificationHubAuthorizationRules cmdlet sets a NotificationHub Authorization Rule.
